The police in Lagos are still searching for the parents of two children rescued from suspected child traffickers in the city. The Lagos State Police Command had arrested Chukwunonso Blessing, a 30-year-old woman, in whose possession the kids were found and made a call for the children’s parents to be identified and located. 



